    {
      "label": "Content description",
      "value": "Commercial letter mentioning a partnership, possibly in relation to some goods or money that has to be dealt with after one of the partners has left (l. 2). The sender also mentions money that was part of a deposit (l. 3) and whih the sender will deliver to the addressee (l. 7) together with some fifty dinars (ll. 8-10). A request from the addressee is followed by a blessing (ll. 5 and 6). The sender asks the addressee to send him a letter use two different formulae (ll. 6 and 7). The letter ends with greetings."
    },
